results.occurrenceRemarks: This observation of a male kudu was remarkable because it stood 30 meters away, engaged in a stare-off, and did not flee.  All other kudu I saw in the area (certainly to the west of this point) reacted much more strongly to people.  I took this as a sign of an unhunted animal, sufficiently near the game reserve.
